root: ^CHEMIST: Where do you think you're going?
^ME: Well this is off to a good start.
^ME: I'm from the Bio-Engineering department upstairs. We are working on increasing the efficiency of growing crops on the lunar surface.
^CHEMIST: Ah, so you are a farmer? I didn't know there were any farmers in our section.
^ME: So I need some of the nitrogen you guys have been stockpiling.
^CHEMIST: I'm afraid not. We need it all ourselves. Now if you could please go away.
